title: Hanna-Barbera Classics:  Moby Dick Adventure Cartoons
description:
Moby Dick cartoons originally aired along with "Mighty Mightor" cartoons.  Two boys, a seal, and a large white whale having undersea adventures.  The episodes in this torrent are:

Moby Dick Intro

The Iguana Men

The Sand Creatures

The Undersea World

Toadus, Ruler of the Dead Ships

The Iceberg Monster
